managements discussion and analysis
j.p. morgan chase & co.
overview
j.p. morgan chase & co. is a leading global financial services firm with
assets of $759billion and operations in more than 50 countries. the firm
serves more than 30million consumer customers and the worlds most prominent
corporate, institutional and government clients. the firms wholesale
businesses are comprised of the investment bank, treasury & securities
services, investment management & private banking and jpmorgan partners. chase
financial services is composed of the firms retail and middle market
businesses.
financial performance of jpmorgan chase
as of or for the year ended december 31,
