j.p. morgan chase & co./2002 annual report
jpmorgan partners
jpmorgan partners, the global private equity organization of jpmorgan
chase, provides equity and mezzanine capital financing to private
companies. it is a diversified investor, investing in buyouts, growth
equity and venture opportunities across a variety of industry sectors,
with the objective of creating long-term value for the firm and
third-party investors.
